go_data.justification: GEF for Rho, p115RhoGEF, has been shown to interact with Galpha12 and Galpha13.
GEF is regulated by Galpha12 and Galpha13, which are part of G-protein coupled receptor signaling.
RhoGEF, like p115RhoGEF, is expected to be located in the cytosol where it can interact with Rho GTPases.
